Scratchpad

所属: FirefoxDeveloperEdition

Unlike the Web Console, which is designed for interpreting a single line of code at a time,
Scratchpad lets you edit larger chunks of JavaScript code,
then execute it in various ways depending on how you want to use the output.


https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Tools/Scratchpad


Mac下操作:
    - 调出:
        1) 快捷键: shift + fn + f4, 打开新窗口
        2) Tools -> Web Developer -> Scratchpad, 打开新窗口
        3) 在Developer Tools 配置面板 -> Default Developer Tools -> 勾选Scratchpad,
           之后即可在开发者工具中看到,不需另外打开窗口,
           不足: 一些功能只能在窗口时才能看到,(Mac桌面顶端)
    - 代码自动补全:
        快捷键: ctrl + space
    - 查看代码/函数文档(Inline documentation):
        快捷键: ctrl + shift + space